Bots Life NFT on Solana is about Deviant bots realizing that their purpose is not just to
work, but bots can enjoy life too and do fun things. The NFTs will allow holders to play a tactical robot
racing battle game about the power struggle between Deviant and Hoax bots. The two robot
syndicates vie to rule the world left behind by humans wiped out by a pan-universe-demic virus. The
5,999 unique bot NFTs will belong to 3 syndicates.
